OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779217874
OL,3,CInside Therme: The green promise
OL,4,Cbehind world's biggest spa
OL,6,FAs Manchester prepares to welcome what
OL,7,Fis billed as the world's largest
OL,8,Fwellbeing resort, attention is turning
OL,9,Fnot just to its scale ` but to its
OL,10,Fenvironmental impact.
OL,12,FThe Austrian company behind Therme
OL,13,Fsays its vision goes beyond luxury,
OL,14,Fpositioning the development as part of
OL,15,Fa global effort to reconnect cities
OL,16,Fwith nature while improving public
OL,17,Fhealth.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
