PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779217874
OL,3,CInside Therme: The green promise
OL,4,Cbehind world's biggest spa
OL,6,FWith similar resorts already operating
OL,7,Fin Bucharest and planned for cities
OL,8,Fincluding Toronto, Washington and
OL,9,FDubai, the model seems to be rapidly
OL,10,Fgaining momentum.
OL,12,FAt the heart of Therme's green
OL,13,Fcredentials is how it claims to manage
OL,14,Fwater ` a crucial issue for a facility
OL,15,Fbuilt around vast warm lagoons and
OL,16,Ftropical environments.
OL,18,FThe company says its thermal pools are
OL,19,Fpowered by renewable energy and
OL,20,Fcleaned using ozone gas, significantly
OL,21,Freducing the need for chlorine.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779217874
OL,3,CInside Therme: The green promise
OL,4,Cbehind world's biggest spa
OL,6,FTherme produces ozone gas on site by
OL,7,Fsplitting oxygen molecules. The gas is
OL,8,Fthen bubbled through the water,
OL,9,Fallowing the entire system to be
OL,10,Fcleaned in just a few hours.
OL,12,F"You can see the bubbles ` that's
OL,13,F99.9% ozone gas," explained Nicolaie
OL,14,FCorbeanu, Technical Director at Therme
OL,15,FBucharest. "It's one of the most
OL,16,Fpowerful processes for cleaning and
OL,17,Fdisinfection."
OL,19,FSo confident is he in the system, he
OL,20,Fclaims the water is "clean enough to
OL,21,Fdrink."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779217874
OL,3,CInside Therme: The green promise
OL,4,Cbehind world's biggest spa
OL,6,FBehind the scenes, technology is also
OL,7,Fused to carefully manage the resort's
OL,8,Fvast indoor ecosystem. Each of the
OL,9,Fthousands of palm trees ` more than
OL,10,F1,500 are planned for Manchester ` is
OL,11,Ffitted with sensors to monitor
OL,12,Fhumidity, temperature and water usage.
OL,14,F"Every tree has its own address,"
OL,15,FCorbeanu said. "We know exactly how
OL,16,Fmuch water and nutrients it receives."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
