OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779217874
OL,3,CInside Therme: The green promise
OL,4,Cbehind world's biggest spa
OL,6,FWhen it opens - with 2028 the target
OL,7,Fyear - Therme Manchester will house
OL,8,Faround 800,000 tropical plants and
OL,9,Fmaintain a year-round temperature of
OL,10,F33 degrees. All will be powered, the
OL,11,Fcompany says, by a mix of solar energy
OL,12,Fand heat storage systems designed to
OL,13,Freduce greenhouse gas emissions.
OL,15,FBut with millions of litres of water
OL,16,Frequired to run the pools, questions
OL,17,Fremain about what this could mean for
OL,18,Flocal resources ` particularly during
OL,19,Fperiods of drought or water
OL,20,Frestrictions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779217874
OL,3,CInside Therme: The green promise
OL,4,Cbehind world's biggest spa
OL,6,FProfessor David Russell, Chief
OL,7,FExecutive of Therme Manchester,
OL,8,Finsists the impact will be minimal.
OL,10,F"We're fortunate that there is
OL,11,Fsignificant rainfall in the UK,
OL,12,Fparticularly in the Lake District," he
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"Around 92% of the water we use is
OL,16,Frecycled. Everything we're doing has
OL,17,Fclimate and ecological considerations
OL,18,Fat its core."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779217874
OL,3,CInside Therme: The green promise
OL,4,Cbehind world's biggest spa
OL,6,FHe added that the resort would not
OL,7,Fdrive up household bills ` and could
OL,8,Feven help improve efficiency in the
OL,9,Fwider system.
OL,11,FThe development comes amid a broader
OL,12,Fshift towards wellness-focused
OL,13,Fleisure, with younger generations
OL,14,Fincreasingly opting for health and
OL,15,Frelaxation over traditional nightlife.
OL,16,FTherme's blend of water parks, saunas
OL,17,Fand relaxation spaces ` including
OL,18,Fcinema-style sauna experiences ` is
OL,19,Fdesigned to appeal across age groups.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
