OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779217874
OL,3,CInside Therme: The green promise
OL,4,Cbehind world's biggest spa
OL,6,FThe project has also attracted
OL,7,Fattention at the highest level, with
OL,8,FKing Charles ` a long-time advocate
OL,9,Ffor environmental causes ` invited to
OL,10,Fattend the opening.
OL,12,FAs construction continues in Trafford,
OL,13,Fthe promise is bold: to bring a
OL,14,Ftropical, beach-like escape to one of
OL,15,Fthe UK's rainiest cities, while
OL,16,Fmaintaining strong environmental
OL,17,Fstandards.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
